<h1>Pizza_Dashboard!</h1>
🍕📊 This project has been an incredible learning experience, blending data analysis, visualization, and storytelling to uncover actionable insights.

<u>Key Insights from the Dashboard:</u>

🔥 #KPI :- Total Pizza Sold, Total Revenue, Total Orders, Average Pizza Per Orders and Average Order Value.
📆 #Daily and #Monthly Trends for Total Orders
🍕 Percentage of Sales by #Pizza_Category
💡 Percentage of Sales By #Pizza_Size and Total sold pizzas based on #Pizza_Category
📍 Regional trends, showing how customer preferences vary by #Location.

This dashboard aims to provide a comprehensive tool for decision-making and drive strategies for improving customer satisfaction and business growth.
